summary: Just a refugee of a caravan, nothing much.
descriptionHtml: Dro' Jhana is a refugee from a trading caravan and doesn't say anything, she made home at the frostfruit inn in Rorikstead. As I said she says nothing but a small phrase. This is just to add new interesting npcs. This is my first mod so please don't get upset if it doesn't please you, But more of these npcs are to come! So Enjoy!
author: snipeisbest
